summary: this mod changes the home \"breeze home\" into the blue palace.  i had to do lots of trial and error things so this took me a few hours.
descriptionHtml: This is one of the first mods i have made and it took me a while because i am new.  and with new people making their first mods there will be some problems...  this mod can bug part of the game and not let you enter some places. i would be happy if someone fixes those problems but just give a little credit to me.
author: baconator118
